headline: What Makes Williams-Sonoma (WSM) a New Buy Stock
summary: Williams-Sonoma (WSM) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.

headline: What Drives Investors?
summary: The market yawned at Nvidia's 94% growth and cheered as Williams-Sonoma posted year-over-year declines. It's all about expectations.
